Class UserFetchInf

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.shiftac.upartier.data.IDFetchInf
      • com.github.shiftac.upartier.data.UserFetchInf
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PacketGenerator, ByteArrayIO

    public class UserFetchInf
extends IDFetchInf
    When fetching user information, following situations are possible to occur:

    1. Fetching a user from its ID.
    2. Fetching a user who issued a specified post.
    3. Fetching a list of users belong to a post.
